<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<I c="LootActions" i="action" m="interactions.utils.loot" n="loot_WorldEp21_AskAboutGoldworld" s="490277">
  <L n="loot_actions">
    <V t="notification_and_dialog">
      <U n="notification_and_dialog">
        <V n="dialog" t="notification">
          <U n="notification">
            <V n="icon" t="enabled">
              <V n="enabled" t="participant">
                <U n="participant">
                  <L n="participant_type">
                    <E>TargetSim</E>
                  </L>
                </U>
              </V>
            </V>
            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x70F881EF<!--String: "Ondarion has seen all sorts of people rise and fall from power. Finding an opening to climb up the ladder can be difficult, but every now and then a newcomer manages it."--></T>
                  <T>0x65FBD2E1<!--String: "There's a lot of legends about this place. Most of them are huge exaggerations. But some people genuinely swear they glanced at their future inside a fancy mirror."--></T>
                  <T>0xED66727E<!--String: "Building a powerful Dynasty looks appealing to many up-and-coming Nobles, but be careful making Rivals along the way. Grudges can last for a long time here, just ask our local families."--></T>
                  <T>0xAE4CA4A<!--String: "People say there's loads of hidden passages under Ondarion, and they can lead to the wildest places. Not sure how true it is, but it certainly sounds thrilling."--></T>
                  <T>0x4E25626D<!--String: "Oh, this is a peaceful place. For the most part. Kind of. Well, sometimes. It's been a bit tumultuous since we lost our old beloved monarch."--></T>
                  <T>0xCDCB9F82<!--String: "Family names can mean a lot in Ondarion—they can be a quick path to power. Some people even try to fake theirs!"--></T>
                  <T>0xE3368B9B<!--String: "People here don't really hesitate to draw their sword. Duels can be a swift solution to several different problems. That is if you win, of course."--></T>
                  <T>0xA6497A6E<!--String: "Ondarion is full of secrets, and people here do love to gossip. No one is safe from it. I've heard one of the regulars at the bar in Verdemar seems to know all of the latest Scandals."--></T>
                  <T>0x3B67CDD9<!--String: "Sometimes people find strange small chests in the weirdest parts of Ondarion. It's said they're from a local pirate band that buries them around."--></T>
                  <T>0xC5B1055B<!--String: "Ondarion has eyes and ears everywhere. If you don't want to get caught doing something to cause a Scandal...make sure you're home, alone, and with no one around to see!"--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
          </U>
        </V>
      </U>
    </V>
    <V t="buff">
      <U n="buff">
        <U n="buff">
          <T n="buff_type">490278<!--Buff: buff_Ep21World_Landmarks_AskAboutGoldworldCooldown--></T>
        </U>
      </U>
    </V>
  </L>
</I>